io.confluent.ksql.util

Annotation Type Sandbox


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Sandbox
    Indicates that the target class is a Sandbox, and any invocations on this instance will not affect the core engine state.
    See Also:
    SandboxUtil
